112
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,080
Yes.

113
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:06,470
Open it.

114
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,640
(Be Careful)
We wasted so much time just for this?

115
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:18,280
Oh no, we fell into a trap.

116
